Class SWRLB

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.vocabulary.SWRLB
public class SWRLB extends Object
Vocabulary defining builtin SWRL entities, that have implicit type swrl:Builtin. Created by @szz on 12.03.2019.

See also OWLAPI-api org.semanticweb.owlapi.vocab.SWRLVocabulary
